         <div type="translation">
            <ab>In the granary of the village of Karanis, Kopres, son of Priscus, has shifted to the harbor of Kerke, of the crop of year 19, through Sotas the donkey-driver, 4 donkeys of barley. Phamenoth 16.</ab>
